#WhatsNewAtWestside: Be Bold

"Chisel out all the lives you have hidden within this one. Beneath the layer of the obligatory one might be buried the defiant kind. The one that knows a ‘Sorry’ is as precious as a ‘Thank you’. Uncover the weird one. The kind that cracks silly jokes, breaks into a laugh and doesn’t feel awkward at the end. Pull out the quiet one from the loud one, the type that wants to observe each breath. Sculpt the loud-mouth, big heart, innocent one too. Etch the simple one out from the one that loves complexities. The kind that knows not all battles have to be fought.

And when you have bargained and explored, failed and admired with as many, carve the life you dream of. The one you deserve. For all your lives are queued up in anticipation of when you’ll birth them into meaning."

- @deepakramola X @westsidestores
